data.description: **Price Reduced** A perfect blend of ease, comfort and convenience, this ZERO STEP entry, 1-bedroom, 1-bath, HANDICAP ACCESSIBLE Central Park Condo was tastefully updated in 2020! New cabinets, counters, tiled shower, flooring, paint, bedroom window, all-in-one washer dryer and more! Enjoy the cozy fireplace, spacious bedroom, large closet, kitchen eating bar, 2 ACs & in-unit laundry. Relax on the private balcony and watch Spokane Indian fireworks! This well maintained community is conveniently located between Downtown Spokane and Spokane Valley, offering quick access to I-90, Dishman Hills trails, hospitals, restaurants & shopping. Community amenities include 2 pools, jacuzzi hot tub, saunas, Clubhouse, fitness room, pool table & more. Assigned covered parking is right out front and a small storage unit is off balcony. Low monthly Condo/HOA fee ($229) includes water, sewer, garbage, lawn care, building maintenance and snow removal. All appliances stay.
